From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: hejuworld-droid <hejuworld-droid@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Thu, 22 May 2026 00:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] AN400: Change bootdelay to 3 for U-Boot console interrupt

The original kvim4_defconfig sets BOOTDELAY=2 which is too short
for reliable U-Boot console access. Change to 3 seconds to allow
users to interrupt boot and access U-Boot command line.

This patch is applied after the official Update-kvim4_defconfig.patch.
---
 board/khadas/defconfigs/kvim4_defconfig | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/board/khadas/defconfigs/kvim4_defconfig b/board/khadas/defconfigs/kvim4_defconfig
index 515d1471..aaaaaaaa 100644
--- a/board/khadas/defconfigs/kvim4_defconfig
+++ b/board/khadas/defconfigs/kvim4_defconfig
@@ -15,7 +15,7 @@ CONFIG_ARMV8_CRYPTO=y
 CONFIG_DEBUG_UART=y
 # CONFIG_ANDROID_BOOT_IMAGE is not set
 CONFIG_OF_BOARD_SETUP=y
 CONFIG_SD_BOOT=y
-CONFIG_BOOTDELAY=2
+CONFIG_BOOTDELAY=3
 CONFIG_BOARD_LATE_INIT=y
 # CONFIG_DISPLAY_CPUINFO is not set
 # CONFIG_DISPLAY_BOARDINFO is not set
